{"tid":682669,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【愛美麗】比堤：阿仙奴得6000萬轉會費乜都做唔到","createTime":"2018-05-29T05:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T06:04:47.000Z","uid":72497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5808ed80abeb5e7e8bd43392321179558d0b04","tid":682669,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"紅軍要買3球星 6000萬鎊搶里昂費基亞<br />\n<br />\n對於艾馬利於今夏僅有6000萬增兵一事，比堤似乎十分不滿，強調「兵工廠」的預算太少，未來難與列強競爭：「如只有這麼少錢，即使你找來世上最好的領隊也難有作為。阿仙奴陣容不差，但難與曼城及利物浦相比，他們需要買入最頂級的球星。」<br />\n<br />\n比堤又質疑阿仙奴的新星政策，指球隊當下需要是當打的球星，「我想叫管理層暫停一年買新人。我們已經有足夠的年青球員。這樣已經15年了，我們需要一些新事物，我們要一些具經驗的好球員﹐令球隊更有個性，這亦是當下欠缺的。對我來說6000萬轉會費簡直是笑話。」（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=MFJqdupFcKWnelv73%2FLeouargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=ed520c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"97c0831a00f09c1ee4553921fcffe52920375e88","tid":682669,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"想信愛帥冇問題！"},{"pid":"ca345ddb2a407a3f295fa279284687d40c02bdd0","tid":682669,"uid":45335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"美麗：冇錢？冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高層：幾時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66f7bcb1947138230996bbfb6154d3464a49eb6","tid":682669,"uid":37948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴: 比堤剛加盟阿狗時什麼也不是"},{"pid":"8b6e96670f4c50e37f97918bd4655ef4d6e86d56","tid":682669,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c66f7bcb1947138230996bbfb6154d3464a49eb6","tid":682669,"uid":37948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴: 比堤剛加盟阿狗時什麼也不是"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:04:47.000Z","msg":"係"}]}